{"id":1254135,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Sumire Morohoshi is a Japanese voice actress affiliated with Himawari Theatre Group.","name":"Sumire Morohoshi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"诸星堇是日本的女性声优、歌手，1999年生于神奈川县，所属事务所为剧团向日葵。\n\n艺名是本名。父母当初打算起的名字不是“堇”，而是“莉樱（莉桜／りおん）”。但是，由于刚出生时候的诸星右半身麻痹，自己也不能喝牛奶。所以如果一生都是麻痹状态的话就要使自己的名字写起来简单，于是名字改成了平假名。但是，麻痹只是暂时的，出生后数月就消失了。\n\n3岁的时候进入向日葵剧团。入团的契机之一，是对《千与千寻》中的汤婆婆这一角色产生憧憬，并对父母称希望自己成为那样的声优。\n\n2006年，在7岁时出演《血色花园》的凯莉，被共演的子安武人的声调转换演技所折服，从那个时候开始产生了专业的自觉。\n\n9岁时出演《钢之炼金术师 FULLMETAL ALCHEMIST》的角色妮娜·塔克，由于产生了与年幼声质相反的出色演技而备受朴璐美、钉宫理惠及内海贤二等人的好评。\n\n崇拜的声优是为她所看过的吹替版《孟汉娜》配音的白石凉子。\n\n2018年4月开始进入大学就读。\n\n2019年5月31日，宣布将于秋季歌手solo出道。","name":"诸星堇","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"hi","name":"हिन्दी","english_name":"Hindi","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"諸星堇是日本的女性聲優、演員、歌手、前童星。出身於神奈川縣足柄上郡大井町，畢業於青山學院大學，所屬經紀公司為向日葵劇團，所屬唱片公司為 Flying DOG。","name":"諸星堇","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"諸星すみれ","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"סומירה מורוהושי","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"모로호시 스미레","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"สึมิเระ โมโรโฮชิ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Sumire Morohoši","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Sumire Morohoshi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Sumire Morohoshi es una actriz de voz japonesa (seiyuu) que está afiliada a la compañía de teatro Himawari.","name":"Sumire Morohoshi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Сумирэ Морохоси","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"سومير موروهوشي","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Суміре Морохоші","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"諸星堇，童星出身，是日本的女性聲優、演員、歌手。出身於神奈川縣，所屬公司為向日葵劇團。","name":"諸星堇","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Sumire Morohoshi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"سومیره موروهوشی","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Sumire Morohoshi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ID","iso_639_1":"id","name":"Bahasa indonesia","english_name":"Indonesian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Sumire Morohoshi","primary":false}}]}